title: There's No Condom For Your Heart // Relationship Goals Reloaded (Part 9)
description:
Do you feel tied to your past? Sometimes our past sins can entangle us if we don’t take it to God. Are you struggling with soul ties?

Today Pastor Mike illustrated an example that helped us learn about the power of sex, soul ties, and how we can use our past hurt to impact the world with our testimonies! Check out week 9 of Relationship Goals Reloaded!”
